  "returns": "Array of body properties (see Remarks )",
  "remarks": "The material values returned include the face color (R,G,B values), reflectivity (ambient, diffuse, specular, shininess), transparency, and emission. Valid values are from 0 to 1 for all variables.\nIf the return value is -1 values, then material property values are not assigned to the feature.\nThe format of the return value is an array of doubles as follows:\n[\nR, G, B, Ambient, Diffuse, Specular, Shininess, Transparency, Emission\n]",
